Package cz.cuni.mff.kocur.influence

Package that contain influence maps implementation.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PropagationFunction<T>
    A interface that represents a function that can be used for propagating the influence.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BotContextualLayer
    If we are working with agent, most of it's influence layers will be moving with him and will represents his surroundings.
    DireThreatLayer
    Dire threats layer.
    EnemyCreepInfluence
    Class that represents a enemy creep's influence (from our agent's perspective).
    EnemyHeroInfluence
    This class represents a propagation function that spreads influence of enemy heroes on the influence map (from agent's perspective).
    EnemyThreatsLayer
    Threat layer that is generated for Lina using her context.
    EnemyTowerInfluencePropagation
    Class that represents a propagation function that spreads enemy towers influence (from the agent's perspective).
    EntityParameterWithInfluence
    Our extension of entity parameter.
    ExtendedAgentContext
    Abstract class that extends AgentContext.
    FarmingInfluence<T extends cz.cuni.mff.kocur.world.BaseEntity>
    Class that represents farming influence propagation function.
    FarmingLayer
    Layer that represents farming influence.
    FortPropagation<T extends cz.cuni.mff.kocur.interests.Fort>
    Propagation function that propagates fort's influence across the map.
    FOWLayer
    Layer that stores our field of view inside the influence map.
    FOWPropagation<T extends cz.cuni.mff.kocur.world.BaseEntity>
    Propagates hero's field of view to influence map.
    FriendlyHeroInfluence
    Class that spreads influence of friendly heroes (from the agent's perspective).
    FriendlyThreatsLayer
    Class that stores friendly (from the agent's perspective) threats to the influence layer.
    FrontLine
    Class that represents a front line.
    GoalLayer
    Layers that stores goals inside.
    HeightsLayer
    This layer represents heights.
    InfluenceLayer  
    InfluenceLayerTemplates
    Class that stores influence layers, that do not change during the application.
    InterestParameterWithInfluence
    Class that represents a parameter, an interest object can use to spread its influence etc.
    LinearRadiusPropagationFunction<T extends cz.cuni.mff.kocur.world.BaseEntity>
    Propagation function that is based on linear faloff.
    MinMaxObject
    Object that stores minimum, maximum and its locations.
    MyCreepInfluence
    Propagation function, that spreads influence of agent's friendly creeps.
    MyTowerInfluencePropagation
    Propagates influence of tower, that belongs to my team (from the agent's perspective).
    ParamsBuilder
    A builder that builds agent's parameters.
    PolynomialAttackRangePropagationFunction<T extends cz.cuni.mff.kocur.world.BaseEntity>
    Influence spreading function, that is given by polynomial.
    PropagationPoint
    Class that defines a point, where we spread during the wave propagation.
    RadiantThreatLayer
    Class that represents radiant threats.
    WavePropagationFunction<T extends cz.cuni.mff.kocur.base.Location>
    This is a representation of "bfs" like propagation function.
    WavePropagationWithContext<T extends cz.cuni.mff.kocur.base.Location>
    This class extends a WavePropagationFunction (WPF).
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InfluenceCombinationException
    Exception caused by combining different layers.
